                              |                         SCL (A5)|       | (5V DC)           |
+---------------------+       |                                 |       +-------------------+
| MH-Z19B (UART)      |------>| Software RX (D2)                |
| (5V DC)             |<------| Software TX (D3)                |                                     +------------------------+ 
+---------------------+       |                                 |       +---------------------+       |     ESP8266 Wi-Fi      |       +--------------------+
                              |                       HW TX (D1)|------>| Logic Level         |------>|RXD (RX)                |------>| ThingSpeak Cloud   |
+---------------------+       |                                 |       | Shifter (5V -> 3.3V)|       |       (3.3V DC. )      |       |      (Wi-Fi)       |
| LDR (Analog A0)     |------>| Analog 0 (A0)                   |       |                     |       |                        |       +--------------------+
| (5V DC Circuit)     |       |                       HW RX (D0)|<------|                     |<------|TXD (TX)                |
+---------------------+       |                                 |       +---------------------+       +------------------------+ 
                              |                                 |
+---------------------+       |                                 |
| Soil Moisture       |------>| Analog 1 (A1)                   |
| (Analog A1)         |       |                                 |
+---------------------+       +---------------------------------+
